# 🎓 School Collections Platform

A backend service that enables schools to collect tuition and other school-related payments through flexible installment plans powered by ALATPay.

---

## 🚀 Project Overview

The School Collections Platform helps schools manage fee collections while giving parents the flexibility to pay in installments.

Instead of requiring one-time payments, schools can configure installment plans, generate payment links, receive real-time payment updates via ALATPay webhooks, and automatically notify parents through WhatsApp.

---

## ✨ Features

### MVP

- Student Management
- Collection Plan Management
- Installment Generation
- ALATPay Payment Integration
- Webhook Processing
- Payment Tracking
- Dashboard APIs
- WhatsApp Notifications

