## 🚀 Getting Started

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone <repository-url>
```

Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

Create `.env`

```env
DATABASE_URL=
PORT=5000
```

Generate Prisma Client

```bash
npx prisma generate
```

Run migrations

```bash
npx prisma migrate dev
```

Start development server

```bash
npm run dev
```

